  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There are many ways to reduce stress. This study will compare 2 different programs for
      reducing stress. In addition to looking at how well the programs reduce stress, we will also
      ask questions about how these programs may be working.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
